### **`.gitignore`**

This `.gitignore` file is designed to ignore unnecessary files and directories for both the frontend (React) and backend (Python) parts of your project.

```gitignore
# Python
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
__pycache__/
venv/
*.sqlite3
.env

# Flask and Python bytecode
instance/
*.log

# React
node_modules/
build/
coverage/
*.env
*.eslintcache
*.cache
*.gitmodules

# Docker
*.dockerignore
docker-compose.override.yml

# IDEs and Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Windows
Thumbs.db

# Environment variables
.env

# pytest
.cache/

# VSCode settings
.vscode/
